{"tid":2011142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"會搭黨鐵嘅入黎（唔係要鬧你）","createTime":"2020-05-10T20:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T12:49:02.000Z","uid":76224,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d18899f8d69fb2dec11c16c1e2f5ef6fd77dbe82","tid":2011142,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:14:20.000Z","msg":"我知道有好多人都仲會去搭黨鐵，一定有各種原因/藉口。但我希望大家可以將哩個行為變得有意義d。<br />\n<br />\n文宣從來都唔應該以已經醒左嘅人做受眾，搭黨鐵嘅有好大多數都係藍絲/港豬，而佢地就係文宣嘅主要目標。每一個黨鐵站，每一架列車，每一個車箱，都係一塊大型廣告牌。<br />\n<br />\n希望仍然選擇搭黨鐵嘅人，可以自備一d野去搭。而有做開文宣嘅人，可以嘗試下其他廣告牌。"},{"pid":"a830a7337515536fd696e17b3c65e4fe5dbfab72","tid":2011142,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:15:02.000Z","msg":"會搭黨鐵嘅入黎（唔係要鬧你）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2011142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2011142</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9eeb08ef96f3f343323a9a45c063a87acb3a402a","tid":2011142,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:19:51.000Z","msg":"會搭黨鐵嘅入黎（唔係要鬧你）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2011142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2011142</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"07566d743d714b04da519bb5b8c970b9b521e91e","tid":2011142,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T20:29:37.000Z","msg":"會搭黨鐵嘅入黎（唔係要鬧你）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2011142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2011142</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"950a9831e18ba272edff69a9049d8679a2ca55ee","tid":2011142,"uid":193788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持<br />\n<br />\n大西北拎入屯門有時真係冇得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a654db7c43b51c1bba23e497d1f186f9e88afc88","tid":2011142,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r